<p><span class="anchor" id="p64"></span>رَجْعِيَّة لَا مختلعة<a href="#p64" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p65"></span>فَلَا يلْحقهَا طَلَاق وان كَانَت<a href="#p65" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>